{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"3256cfef27","title":"向学校党政提出九点要求","origin":"《右派言行集(下集)》 (全校学生中部分右派言行)，中共云南大学委员会编，一九五七年九月。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"242a737b4c","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"3256cfef27"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"2499a730cb","name":"云南大学"},{"id":"5b75e5fc9f","name":"徐乃宁"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"4d02c5e96f","type":"title","text":"向学校党政提出九点要求","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3256cfef27"},{"id":"263e674b30","type":"authors","text":"云南大学徐乃宁","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3256cfef27"},{"id":"c774ea3977","type":"subtitle","text":"向学校党政提出九点要求  　　林学系三年级  徐乃宁","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3256cfef27"},{"id":"83cfc0fddd","type":"paragraph","text":"(一)扩大校内民主，实行校务委员会制，防止以党代政的作法。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3256cfef27"},{"id":"e4901955a7","type":"paragraph","text":"(二)实行学分制，采取自由听课制。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3256cfef27"},{"id":"7581d572eb","type":"paragraph","text":"(三)取消口试制，取消五级记分制，实行百分制。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3256cfef27"},{"id":"f73709c46f","type":"paragraph","text":"(四)选修外国语。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3256cfef27"},{"id":"2b87e05440","type":"paragraph","text":"(五)教师讲课中贯彻“百家争鸣”，全面介绍世界科学成就。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3256cfef27"},{"id":"6c76e03f0d","type":"paragraph","text":"(六)每班由学校订光明日报一份至数份。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3256cfef27"},{"id":"8139fbe8ad","type":"paragraph","text":"(七)党、团、群必须一视同仁，除组织内部事务外，一般问题应同时向师生员工传达(如五四年棉布计划供应的报告，先向党团内传达后向群众传达。)避免人为的制造墙和沟。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3256cfef27"},{"id":"b63643f86e","type":"paragraph","text":"(八)毕业生分配应以才为先，不以党团员为先，并根据先生和本人意见。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3256cfef27"},{"id":"45b63acbc7","type":"paragraph","text":"(九)及时处理肃反遗留下的评(平)反问题。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3256cfef27"}],"page":{"id":"0d2354c1e5","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3256cfef27","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}